curl -XPOST 'http://localhost:9200/electronic_products/_create/5779' -H 'Content-Type: application/json' -d '{"product_name": "SGM8271/SGM8272/SGM8274", "table_name": "GENERAL DESCRIPTION", "content": "GENERAL DESCRIPTION  The SGM8271 (single), SGM8272 (dual) and SGM8274  (quad) are high precision operational amplifiers, which  are optimized for high voltage operation from 4.5V to 36V  single supply or ±2.25V to ±18V dual power supplies.  They provide a wide input common mode voltage range  and rail-to-rail output voltage swing.  Furthermore, the SGM8271/2/4 provide high slew rate,  low bias current, low offset current, low offset voltage  and low offset voltage drift.  The SGM8271 is available in Green SOT-23-5,  MSOP-8 and SOIC-8 packages. The SGM8272 is  available in Green SOIC-8 and MSOP-8 packages. The  SGM8274 is available in Green SOIC-14 and TSSOP-14  packages. They are specified over the extended -40℃  to +125℃ temperature range.    "}'
